{"tid":1324723,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"搞鳩新鴻基喺一定要繼續做","createTime":"2019-07-16T15:48:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-17T05:05:11.000Z","uid":52609,"like":19,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9f871eb761645e208d97effd2798f2fd62eaad6b","tid":1324723,"uid":52609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T15:48:07.000Z","msg":"搞鳩新鴻基、TVB同其他藍絲商家喺要比全世界知道<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">犯香港人者，雖遠必誅</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n令其他中立、欺善怕惡、淺藍、深藍嘅市民<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">唔敢得罪香港人</span></strong><br />\n佢地<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">唔敢出聲就可以形成沉默大多數支持我地嘅狀態</span></strong><br />\n甚至可以令到啲勝利市民轉過黎支持我地<br />\n可以繼續滾雪球，積累民意<br />\n<br />\n不過當然要記得最重要嘅<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">721 金鐘見<br />\n<br />\n兄弟爬山 各自努力<br />\n不分化 不篤灰 不割蓆 不譴責</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"bed84bebe41aad9a921a06bae8b7d2e1e77add51","tid":1324723,"uid":52609,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T15:48:25.000Z","msg":"前新城市職員，大家聽我講兩句<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/RxKLgU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/RxKLgU</a><br />\n<br />\n新城市好驚俾人知三樓係公眾通道<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1324439\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1324439</a>"},{"pid":"bd33fa8dabd3b97c9ff01a3cd18da2dfd1b84202","tid":1324723,"uid":52609,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T15:49:36.000Z","msg":"Group link <br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/DTvoRUcwJ90Wva6Pffa8ww\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FDTvoRUcwJ90Wva6Pffa8ww&d=4wcocBccBPvk8MIeFEbr%2BXQc4T2II2f942UkEibGql8%3D&h=f700a90c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/DTvoRUcwJ90Wva6Pffa8ww</a>"},{"pid":"a66061507ba6628605559afd965c95e713057a16","tid":1324723,"uid":52609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0